room_title: Escape room "Space Station" by Red Button Escape in Miami
room_address: 9705 W Sample Rd. Coral Springs, FL 33065
room_description: You and your crew are aboard a space station in the far reaches of the galaxy. During your mission to collect and catalog new specimens from other planets, something or someone has compromised the space station. The only way to survive now is to get to the escape pod before the space station is destroyed. Work together to escape while you still can!
